(ns app.car
  (:require
   [com.fulcrologic.fulcro.components :as comp :refer [defsc]]
   [com.fulcrologic.fulcro.dom :as dom]))

(defsc Car [this {:car/keys [id name color] :as props}]
  {:query [:car/id :car/name :car/color]
   :initial-state (fn [id name color] {:car/id id
                                       :car/name name
                                       :car/color color})}
  (js/console.log "Props" props)
  (dom/div (dom/p (str name "(" color ")"))))

(def ui-car (comp/factory Car))
